=====================================
To compile sequential version type
make seq
for MPI version type
make mpi

=====================================
The input-files (read when executing)
1) avg_params.dat
2) Romb5.dat
specify the parameters for orientation averaging and Csca calculation;
(1) is self-documented
(2) is rather outdated
